{"tid":615094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華講貿易戰 揀錯背景變咗頭頂屁股","createTime":"2018-04-03T05:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T06:01:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aab1f7e96a706b36837f2c408464331b1e206158","tid":615094,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180403/large/1522731107_98d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180403%2Flarge%2F1522731107_98d8.jpg&h=a3f6e295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國為咗反撃美國，最近公佈對美國128項進口產品加徵15%或25%關稅。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華出席活動嗰陣回應事件，話依家難以分析中美貿易戰對本港嘅具體影響，不過佢講嘢嗰陣企咗喺一幅畫前面，咁啱畫入面個人係倒轉咗嘅，局長個頭一併埋去，就形成「高官與屁股」嘅有趣畫面，所以揀啱背景真係好重要。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華似乎唔知背景出事，繼續解畫，話香港作為中美之間貿易嘅重要轉口地方，有成7%至9%嘅中美貿易會經香港轉口，任何貿易糾紛都會影響呢啲生意，佢希望兩地政府審慎合理咁處理事件，又強調局方一直有同本地商會聯絡，留意清單入面有幾多項同本港有關，再評估對本港嘅影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180403/58028272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58028272&d=DF0wBaBGUr8MGd9%2B%2FFq5Kcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=af21a408\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F58028272&h=c0bbff5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180403/58028272</a>"},{"pid":"8e767c82de6ccd5e7db56b86cc98225718aed71c","tid":615094,"uid":51720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"係人都唔好「被瓜田李下」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9221e6128a3c97882d65093c578494eaa38c3b79","tid":615094,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:50:41.000Z","msg":"邱騰華似乎唔知背景出事，繼續解畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/